TITLE: Episode 145 - The Joys of Being Cancelled with Josh Denny
DESCRIPTION: This week, we are joined by Josh Denny. He's a canceled stand-up comedian, a podcaster, a writer, and a Food Network host. This is a surprisingly topical timing for this episode after the drama Cam got himself into on Twitter. Join us as we talk about his story, Cam's story, and more.
